      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "NEW YORK, Dec. 6.-An organ\nization of men has been formed in\nNew York to take up the fight for\nwoman suffrage. 1t will be known\nas the Mems League for Woman\nSuffrage, and big mass meeting\nis to be held soon to interest other\nmen.\n\n\nG. Foster Peabody is president.\nAmong the vice presidents are Her.\nbert Parsons, Republican leader,\nand William M. WINS, who man\naged Hearst's campaign for mayor."
    }
